      <title>继 2023 年业绩辉煌之后，洲际酒店集团今年将向股东返还超过 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/ihg-return-over-1-bln-shareholders-this-year-after-strong-2023-2024-02-20/</link>
